  "texts": [
    "Precision (prec) is then calculated as |TP| |TP|+|FP| to evaluate the likelihood of making false positive reports.",
    "Consequently, AP is defined as the integration over recall: AP = 1 0 prec (r) dr.• mAP: mAP is calculated by averaging the AP values across different thresholds and categories.",
    "These thresholds are based on IoU typically (like DENSE).",
    "However in NuScenes, the thresholds are center-distance based represented by a set of thresholds D. The overall object category space, denoted as C, is heavily biased and consists of 10 categories.",
    "The mAP can be expressed as:mAP = 1 |C||D| c∈C d∈D AP c,d(3)• NDS: NDS is designed to address the limitations of mAP in capturing all aspects of general detection tasks, such as vehicle velocity."
  ],
